#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today‚Äôs lesson is about helping children follow rules and instructions by using consequences.\n"
"\n"
"Consequences are the good or negative things that happen after a child‚Äôs actions. When children don‚Äôt follow a rule, giving consequences can help them learn and take responsibility for their actions."
msgstr ""
"Isifundo sanamhlanje singokunceda abantwana balandele imithetho kunye nemiyalelo ngokusebenzisa iziphumo.\n"
"\n"
"Iziphumo zizinto ezilungileyo okanye ezimbi ezenzekayo emva kwezenzo zomntwana. Xa abantwana bengawulandeli umthetho ukunika iziphumo kunokubanceda bafunde kwaye bathathe uxanduva ngesenzo sabo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How can calm consequences help you and your family?"
msgstr "Zingakunceda njani wena nosapho lwakho iziphumo ezizolileyo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings everyone.\n"
"\n"
"Even if you do everything right, your child will misbehave sometimes. We may be tempted to scream and shout, but that just leaves everyone more angry. \n"
"\n"
"If we stay calm, and give them a calm consequence, they will learn to take responsibility for their actions instead."
msgstr ""
"Molweni nonke.\n"
"\n"
"Nokuba ungenza yonke into kakuhle, umntwana wakho angaziphatha kakubi ngamanye amaxesha. Singazibona sele sifuna ukukhwaza kwaye singxole, kodwa oko kushiya wonke umntu enomsindo ngakumbi.\n"
"\n"
"Ukuba sihlala sizolile, kwaye sibanike iziphumo ezizolileyo, bazokufunda ukuthatha inxaxheba ngeziphumo zabo."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_5.name,
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Some consequences happen naturally ‚Äì like when a toy breaks, it can‚Äôt be used.\n"
"\n"
"Others are set by you to help your child follow rules (_‚Äúif you don‚Äôt pack away your toys, you can‚Äôt play with them tomorrow‚Äù_). \n"
"\n"
"Let‚Äôs see how @data.characters.f1_father.name uses consequences to help his son, @data.characters.f1_son_5.name, follow instructions:"
msgstr ""
"Ezinye iziphumo ziyazenzekela - ifana nokuba kophuke into yokudlala, ayinakusetyenziswa.\n"
"\n"
"Ezinye zibekiwe nguwe ukunceda umntwana wakho alandele imithetho(_\" ukuba awuzibeki kude izinto zakho zokudlala, awuzokwazi ukudlala ngazo ngomso\"_)\n"
"\n"
"Masijonge ukuba u@data.characters.f1_father.name uzisebenzisa njani iziphumo ukunceda unyana wakhe, u@data.characters.f1_son_5.name alandele imiyalelo:"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_5.name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You are playing so nice and quiet, @data.characters.f1_son_5.name. In 5 minutes, it will be time to clean up your toys."
msgstr "Udlala kamnandi kwaye uthe cwaka, @data.characters.f1_son_5.name. Kwimizuzu eyi 5, izakubalixesha lokucoca izinto zakho zokudlala."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "*5 minutes later*"
msgstr "*emva kwemizuzu eyi 5*"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It‚Äôs time to put away your toys."
msgstr "Lixesha lokubeka kude izinto zakho zokudlala."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No. Not yet!"
msgstr "Hayi. Hayi okwangoku!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_5.name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_son_5.name, either you put away the toys now, or you won‚Äôt be able to play with your toys after dinner."
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_son_5.name, ingaba ubeka kude izinto zakho zokudlala ngoku, okanye awuzokwazi ukudlala ngazo emva kwesidlo sangokuhlwa."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.role_name! should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No, @data.characters.f1_father.role_name! I don‚Äôt want to! I‚Äôm not finished with my game."
msgstr "Hayi, @data.characters.f1_father.role_name! Andifuni! Andikagqibi ngomdlalo wam."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_5.name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Because you did not clean up your toys when I asked you to, @data.characters.f1_son_5.name, you cannot play with your toys after dinner. \n"
"Now please come and wash your hands."
msgstr ""
"Kuba ungakhange uzicoce izinto zakho zokudlala ngexesha ndikuxelela ngalo, @data.characters.f1_son_5.name, awuzokudlala ngezinto zakho zokudlala emva kwesidlo sangokuhlwa.\n"
"Ngoku ndicela uze kwaye uhlambe izandla zakho."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_5.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You are washing your hands so nicely, @data.characters.f1_son_5.name ‚Äì well done!"
msgstr "Uzihlambe kakuhle izandla zakho, @data.characters.f1_son_5.name - wenze kakuhle!"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_5.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_father.name used a consequence to help @data.characters.f1_son_5.name learn that actions have impacts."
msgstr "U@data.characters.f1_father.name usebenzise iziphumo ukunceda u@data.characters.f1_son_5.name afunde ukuba izenzo zinefuthe."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_5.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"@data.characters.f1_father.name did this by:\n"
"- üòå Staying calm \n"
"- ü§ùüèæ Involving @data.characters.f1_son_5.name in planning the consequence \n"
"- üíú Giving a fair consequence related to the behaviour (no playing after dinner if you don't put toys away) \n"
"- ‚≠ê Being consistent by following through with the consequence"
msgstr ""
"U@data.characters.f1_father.name wenze lento ngoku:\n"
"- üòå Hlala ezolile\n"
"- ü§ùüèæ Ngokubandakanya u@data.characters.f1_son_5.name ekucwangciseni iziphumo\n"
"- üíú Ukunika iziphumo ezifanelekileyo ezinxulumene nokuziphatha ( akukho kudlala emva kwesidlo sangokuhlwa ukuba awuzibeki izinto zokudlala)\n"
"- ‚≠ê Ukuhambelana ngokulandela iziphumo"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_5.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How does @data.characters.f1_father.name give @data.characters.f1_son_5.name a consequence?"
msgstr "Ingaba u@data.characters.f1_father.name umnike njani u@data.characters.f1_son_5.name iziphumo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He makes his disappointment clear"
msgstr "Uye wenza ukuphoxeka kwakhe kwacaca"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Try again! @data.characters.f1_father.name explains the consequence in a calm way."
msgstr "Zama kwakhona! U@data.characters.f1_father.name uye wacacisa iziphumo ngomoya ozolileyo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He speaks calmly and explains why he is giving the consequence"
msgstr "Uthethe zolileyo kwaye wacacisa ukuba kutheni enikeza ngeziphumo"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_5.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"That‚Äôs right. @data.characters.f1_father.name shows us that it‚Äôs important to introduce consequences when you are feeling calm and makes sure that @data.characters.f1_son_5.name understands why he can‚Äôt play after dinner. \n"
"There are two right answers! Did you find them?"
msgstr "Ilungile lonto u@data.characters.f1_father.name usibonisa kuba kubalulekile ukwazisa iziphumo xa uziva uzolile kwaye uyaqinisekisa ukuba u@data.characters.f1_son_5.name uyayiqonda kutheni engadlali emveni kwesidlo sangokuhlwa. kukho iimpendulo ezimbini ezichanekileyo! Ubafumene?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He gets a bit angry, but then makes the consequence clear"
msgstr "Uyacaphuka kancinci, kodwa emva koko wenze iziphumo zacaca"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Try again! @data.characters.f1_father.name stays calm."
msgstr "Zama kwakhona!@data.characters.f1_father.name hlala uzolile."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_father.name follows through with the consequence"
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_father.name Landela ngeziphumo"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"That‚Äôs right. @data.characters.f1_father.name shows us that it‚Äôs important to follow through for the consequence to work. \n"
"There are two right answers! Did you find them?"
msgstr ""
"Kulungile.u@data.characters.f1_father.name sibonise ukuba kubalulekile ukulandela ukuze iziphumo zisebenze.\n"
"Kukho iimpendulo ezimbini ezichanekileyo,Ingaba uzifumene?"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_5.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_5.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"What would @data.characters.f1_son_5.name learn if @data.characters.f1_father.name gives in or does not give the consequence? \n"
"\n"
"@data.characters.f1_son_5.name would learn:"
msgstr ""
"Ingaba yintoni u @data.characters.f1_son_5.name azakuyifunda ku @data.characters.f1_son_5.name ukuba uyakunikezela okanye akaniki iziphumo?\n"
"\n"
"@data.characters.f1_son_5.name baya kufunda:"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He can get away with this behaviour in the future"
msgstr "Unako ukubalekela kude kulendlela yokuziphatha kwixesha elizayo"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.role_name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Not to listen when his @data.characters.f1_father.role_name gives instructions"
msgstr "Ukungamameli xa u@data.characters.f1_father.role_name enika imiyalelo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Exactly. It is really important to follow through with what we say, so our children learn boundaries and know they can trust our word."
msgstr "Nqgo / Ngokuchanekileyo. Kubalulekile kakhulu ukulandela oko sikuthethayo, ukuze abantwana bethu bafunde imida kwaye banokuthembela kwilizwi lethu."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That @data.characters.f1_father.name loves him and forgives him"
msgstr "Ukuba u@data.characters.f1_father.name uyamthanda kwaye uyamxolela"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_5.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Try again! @data.characters.f1_son_5.name would actually learn not to take @data.characters.f1_father.name seriously when he gives an instruction, or that he can get away with this behaviour in the future."
msgstr "Zama kwakhona!u@data.characters.f1_son_5.name angafunda ukungamthatheli ngqalelo u@data.characters.f1_father.name xa enika umyalelo,okanye ukuba unokuhamba nale ndlela yokuziphatha kwixesha elizayo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are some easy steps to use consequences when your child does not listen."
msgstr "Nanga amanye amanyathelo alula okusebenzisa iziphumo xa umntwana wakho engamameli."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "BE CALM"
msgstr "ZOLA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Take some deep breaths or walk away from the situation if you need to.\n"
"\n"
"Then, respond in a calm, clear way."
msgstr ""
"Tsala umoya ezantsi, okanye umke kwindawo ukuba ufuna njalo.\n"
"\n"
"Emva koko, phendula ngokuzolileyo, ngendlela ecacileyo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Shouting at our children only makes things worse. It also teaches them that it is okay to treat others like this when they are upset."
msgstr "Ukubangxolisa abantwana bethu kwenza izinto zibe ngakumbi. ikwabafundisa ukuba kulungile ukuphatha abanye ngoluhlobo xa becaphukile."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "BE FAIR"
msgstr "YIBA NOBULUNGISA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Give a consequence connected to the behaviour, and make sure it is something you can follow through with."
msgstr "Nika iziphumo ezinxulumene nokuziphatha kwaye uqiniseke ukuba yinto onokuthi uyilandele."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"For example, if they do not clean up their toys, they cannot play with them the next day (rather than the whole week).\n"
"\n"
"If your child is experiencing a natural consequence for their action (like not being able to play with their toy after breaking it), you might not need to give them an additional consequence."
msgstr ""
"Umzekelo, ukuba abazicoci izinto zabo zokudlala, abanakudlala ngazo ngosuku olulandelayo ( kuneveki yonke).\n"
"\n"
"Ukuba umntwana wakho ufumana isiphumo sendalo ngesenzo sakhe ( njengokungakwazi ukudlala ngento yakhe yokudlala emveni kokuba eyophulile), akudingeki ukumnika esinye isiphumo kwakhona."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "BE CONSISTENT"
msgstr "UKUNGAGUQUGUQUKI"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Follow through with a consequence every time a rule is broken, even if it feels small. Being consistent shows your child you mean what you say and helps them take the rules seriously."
msgstr "Landela ngeziphumo ngalo lonke ixesha kusaphulwa umthetho, nokuba uvakala umncinci. Ukungaguquki kubonisa umntwana wakho ukuba uthetha lento uyithethayo kwaye umncede ayithathele ingqalelo imithetho."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "If you miss a chance to follow through, do not worry ‚Äì just try again next time."
msgstr "Ukuba uphose ithuba lokulandela, sukukhathazeka - zama kwakhona kwixesha elizayo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "INVOLVE THEM"
msgstr "BABANDAKANYE"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask your child what a fair consequence might be if a rule is not followed. This helps them learn responsibility and makes it more likely they will stick to the rule."
msgstr "Buza umntwana wakho ukuba sesiphi isiphumo esifanelekileyo ukuba umthetho awulandelwanga. Oku kunokubanceda bafunde uxanduva kwaye kwenza kubelula ukuba babambelele kumthetho."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "More tips"
msgstr "Ezinye ingcebiso"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You can also involve your child in choosing simple and free rewards for their behaviours. This will encourage them to follow the rules more often!"
msgstr "Unokumbandakanya umntwana wakho ekukhetheni imivuzo elula kwaye esimahla ngokuziphatha kwakhe. Oku kuya kumkhuthaza ukuba alandele imithetho rhoqo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Now that we have learned a few useful tips, let‚Äôs come up with some ideas for reasonable and realistic consequences."
msgstr "Ngoku sifundile ngeengcebiso ezimbalwa eziluncedo, masize neengcebiso ezithile zeziphumo ezifanelekileyo nezinenyani."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Would any of these consequences be helpful for you and your child?"
msgstr "Ingaba enye yezi ziphumo zingaluncedo kakhulu kuwe kunye nomntwana wakho?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "If you are late for dinner, your food will be cold"
msgstr "Ukuba ufike emvakwexesha kwesidlo sangokuhlwa, ukutya kwakho kuzakubanda"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "If you continue splashing water out of the bath, bath time will be over"
msgstr "Ukuba uyaqhubeka uchitha amanzi ngaphandle ebhafini, ixesha lokuhlamba lizakuphela"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "If you break your toy, you will have no toy to play with"
msgstr "Ukuba uyophulile into yakho yokudlala, awuzokuba nayo into yokudlala"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "If you can‚Äôt play close to home where I can see you, then you have to come inside"
msgstr "Ukuba awukwazi ukudlala kufutshane nekhaya apho ndinokubona khona, kumele ungene ngaphakathi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Great. Discuss this (or another) consequence with your child and family, and try it out together."
msgstr "Kulungile. Xoxani lento(okanye enye) iziphumo nomntwana wakho kunye nosapho, kwaye nizame kunye."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "If you do not put away your toys, then you cannot play with them tomorrow morning"
msgstr "Ukuba awuzibeki kude izinto zakho zokudlala, awuzokwazi ukudlala ngazo ngomso kusasa"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Great. Discuss this (or another) consequence with your child and family, and try it out tomorrow."
msgstr "Kulungile. Xoxani lento(okanye enye) iziphumo nomntwana wakho kunye nosapho, kwaye nizame kunye."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "None of these will work in my home"
msgstr "Akukho nenye kwezi eyakusebenza ekhayeni lam"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's okay! Try to think of just one consequence that you feel confident you can follow-through with in a calm way. Try starting with something small."
msgstr "Kulungile! Zama ukucinga ngesiphumo sibesinye oziva uzithembile ukuba ungasilandela ngokuzolileyo. Zama ukuqala ngento encinci."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Your home activity is to discuss one household rule that your child finds hard to follow and agree on a fair consequence together. \n"
"\n"
"Remember, if you praise your child when they follow rules, you will see more positive behaviour in your home."
msgstr ""
"Umsebenzi wakho wasekhaya kukuxoxa ngomgaqo omnye wasekhaya umntwana wakho akufumanisa kunzima ukuwulandela kwaye nivumelane ngesiphumo esifanelekileyo kunye.\n"
"\n"
"Khumbula, ukuba uyamncoma umntwana wakho xa elandela imithetho uya kubona ukuziphatha okulungileyo kwikhaya lakho."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_13.name's should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Agreeing on consequences together works! Tap play to hear @data.characters.media_female_13.name's story"
msgstr "Ukuvumelana ngemiphumela ninonke kuyasebenza! Cofa udlala ukuva @data.characters.media_female_13.name exela ibali lakhe"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @global.app_name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When my children misbehaved, I would sometimes let it go and other times I would shout at them and punish them right away. But the next time they did it again! \n"
"\n"
"@global.app_name helped me understand that I can do things differently. Instead of punishing them, I stay calm and give them a consequence to help them change their behaviour.   \n"
"\n"
"I have seen a huge change in my child‚Äôs behaviour, and I have less stress. I wish I knew this long ago, but it is never too late to start!"
msgstr ""
"Xa abantwana bam beziphatha kakubi, ngamanye amaxesha ndandibayeka, ngamanye amaxesha ndibohlwaye ngoko nangoko. Kodwa kwixesha elizayo baphinda kodwa!\n"
"\n"
"@global.app_name indincedilendaqonda ukuba ndingenza izinto ngokohlukileyo. Endaweni yokubatyhala, ndihlala ndizolile kwaye ndibanika iziphumo zokubanceda batshintshe indlela abaziphatha ngayo.\n"
"\n"
"Ndibone utshintsho olukhulu kwindlela yokuziphatha yomntwana wam, kwaye andinalo noxinzelelo. Akwabe bendizazi kwakudala ezi zinto, kodwa alidlulanga kakhulu ixesha lokuba ndiqalise!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The next time your child does not follow a rule, can you use a fair consequence in a calm way?"
msgstr "Kwixesha elizayo xa umntwana wakho engawulandeli umgaqo, ingaba ungakwazi ukusebenzisa iziphumo ezifanelekileyo ngendlela ezolileyo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Ewe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr "Ndicinga njalo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's great! Remember to take a pause before you give the consequence so that you're able to remain calm, and praise yourself afterwards for a job well done!"
msgstr "Kulungile! Khumbula ukuma kancinci phambi kokuba unike isiphumo ukuze ukwazi ukuhlala uzolile, kwaye zincome emva koko ngomsebenzi wakho owenze kakuhle!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr "Hayi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's okay. Keep trying. It will get easier in time. You can start by considering smaller behaviours that your child struggles with and planning a fair consequence in advance so you're ready."
msgstr "Kulungile. Qhubeka uzame. Kuyakubalula ekuhambeni kwexesha. Ungaqala ngokuqwalasele isimilo esincinci umntwana wakho asokola ngaso kwaye ucwangcise iziphumo ezifanelekileyo kwangaphambili ukuze ube ulungile."

